description.fr: Plus votre SCORE est élevé, plus il y aura de {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} à chaque vague\_! \--- Lorsqu'un {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:one} atteint la dernière ligne\_: Élimine tous les {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} sur sa ligne, {value:l}\_points par {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} éliminés de cette façon.
description.en: The higher your SCORE, the more {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} there are in each wave! \--- When a {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:one} reaches the last line: Eliminates all the {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} on their line. {value:l}\_{l, plural, one[point] other[points]} per {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAMEplural:one} eliminated in this way.
description.es: Cuanto más alta sea tu PUNTUACIÓN, ¡más {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} habrá en cada oleada! \--- Cuando un {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:one} alcanza la última línea: Elimina a todos los {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} en su línea, {value:l}\_puntos por {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} eliminados de esta manera.
description.de: Je höher deine PUNKTE, desto mehr {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} erscheinen pro Welle! \--- Wenn ein {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:one} die letzte Reihe erreicht: Eliminiert alle {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} in seiner Reihe, {value:l}\_Punkte pro auf diese Weise eliminiertem {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME,plural:one}.
description.pt: Quanto maior for sua PONTUAÇÃO, maior será o número de {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} em cada onda! \--- Quando um {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:one} chegar na última linha: Elimine todos os {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} em sua linha, {value:l}\_pontos por {%FAMILY_BWORK_NAME, plural:other} eliminado desta forma.
